Automatically register subsequent acquisitions to a reference.

Installation:

* Dependencies:
- For running the system:
python, virtualenv, freesurfer
- For developing the system:
ACE, nifticlib-2.0.0 (for the vsend testing tool)

* Clone the repo (from inside the NMR center, after you have been
granted access)
git clone git@gitlab:ohinds/auto_register

* Setup the python environment

cd <path to>/auto_register
virtualenv aaenv
source aaenv/bin/activate
pip install git+git://github.com/nipy/nibabel.git

* Run the AutoRegister tool

cd <path to>/auto_register
source aaenv/bin/activate
SetupFreesurfer.sh
./auto_register.py -s <directory to save niftis to> -f | -r <reference image>
(See the help for more options)

* Setup the VSend simulator

cd <path to>/auto_register/test/util/scanner_sim/
make

* Run the VSend simulator

cd <path to>/auto_register/test/util/scanner_sim/
./vsend_nii <path to nii file>
